&lt;h3&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About Emplifi&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://emplifi.io/&quot;&gt;Emplifi&lt;/a&gt; is the only&lt;a href=&quot;https://emplifi.io/platform-overview/&quot;&gt; Autonomous CX platform&lt;/a&gt; unifying social marketing, commerce, and customer care for more than 20,000 brands worldwide. Powered by Fuel AI, built on more than 5T of data, and recognized as a leader by leading industry analysts, Emplifi helps enterprise teams orchestrate connected customer journeys and deliver personalized experiences at scale, turning every customer touchpoint into a competitive advantage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About the Sales Team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Emplifi’s sales team is spread around the globe and helps businesses to scale their digital CX innovations and operations internationally while supporting clients of all sizes. Brand relationships are key to our business but we also work with hundreds of agency and media partners. Our aim is always the same - empower marketers to achieve more, no matter where they are or what industry they’re in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of an international team, you will have the opportunity to work with colleagues from Sydney all the way to Sao Paulo, from New York to Singapore and be part of an ever-growing family. You will be supported in your career by a team of professionals dedicated to your development, so that you can grow as a professional and a social media expert advisor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About the Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Account Executive (“AE”) is a pivotal role within Emplifi’s social sales team. This individual carries an individual quota target and is responsible for driving new business, nurturing existing client relationships, and exploring opportunities for cross-selling and upselling. The Account Executive will have a specific focus on either a geographically-based territory or named account territory, ensuring consistent growth and maximization of revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What You&#39;ll Do Here&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New Business Development:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect and identify new business opportunities within the designated territory or named accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain a robust pipeline of potential clients through networking, research, and referrals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present our digital marketing solutions to potential clients, demonstrating how our services can help meet their business objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Management:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working closely with the Solution Consultant and the Customer Success Manager, the AE will foster and grow relationships with existing clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand clients&#39; business goals, challenges, and needs to identify opportunities for additional products and services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regularly review client campaigns and provide insights, optimization suggestions, and reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-selling and Upselling:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recognize opportunities to offer additional or premium services to current clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the customer success organization and solution consultant to identify the next best solutions for existing clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute a comprehensive sales strategy for the assigned territory or named accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize CRM tools to track interactions, sales progress, and client information&lt;/li&gt;
