&lt;h3&gt;About the Marketing Team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Marketing is the centre of creativity at Emplifi. We are a growing department with an attitude of if you can dream it, you can market it. The marketing team drives powerful initiatives that impact how we are seen by the rest of the world, and ultimately engages prospects and customers on a journey with us. Every role on our team holds a key function in the success of our business. You&#39;ll work alongside skilled marketing experts located across the globe, in addition to collaborating cross-functionally with other teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One thing we can promise is you&#39;ll never get bored. Being in a hyper-growth stage we have so many exciting adventures ahead of us. If you&#39;re looking for a job where you can have a real impact then you&#39;ve come to the right place.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
