&lt;p&gt;You will play a critical role in ensuring Emplifi delivers value beyond the product—creating meaningful customer experiences that strengthen relationships and drive measurable business outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This role can be based in our European Offices in London, Munich or Prague.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What You’ll Do Here&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with leadership across Marketing, Customer Success, Sales, and Product to drive customer engagement, retention, and expansion across Emplifi’s customer base&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product Marketing to develop and execute programs that ensure customers are realizing value from the platform, increasing adoption and long-term retention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive campaigns and initiatives that support cross-sell and upsell opportunities, partnering with Sales and Customer Success to identify and activate expansion opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive reuse of demand generation campaigns and assets for customer audiences, tailoring messaging to support retention and expansion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scale Emplifi’s customer advocacy program, including case studies, testimonials, reviews, and reference management&lt;/li&gt;
